---
title: Mediterranean Garlic & Herb Beef Tacos with Mixed Salad & Garlicky Yoghurt
description: The secret to our colourful, beef tacos is all in the leafy goodness. Substituting Greek yoghurt for mayonnaise lends a great tangy zestiness, and means you can chomp down on these tasty delights guilt free.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mediterranean-garlic-herb-beef-tacos-cbcec7ef.jpg
